An apology if required:
I've been a bit quiet of late. Sorry about that. Sometimes a while goes by when nothing worth making turns up. However. A new book will be out in the next few months – not depressing sci-fi for once – and more stuff is coming, promise. If that's something you're waiting for, then thank you kindly for waiting.
